::Prowl::

"I know you can, love, but I want to help," Prowl replies, swooping 
down toward Iron Raptor. He tensed his talons, ready to grab on to 
her. He hoped she'd forgive him for it.

"I'm coming with you whether you like it or not!" he exclaims, 
striking forward with his talons. Before they could contact, 
something hard hits him in the head.

Not looking ahead of him, he had flown into a branch.

Prowl flips forward over the branch, a crack sounding from his neck 
as he flies into another one, followed by a snap of his wing. He 
transforms and falls to the ground, landing on his stomach as he hits 
several more branches.
